Subject: Live update still available after install
Description:
Good day,

My name is Shawn and I'm reaching out on behalf of Fastco Canada.
After installing the EPP Hotfix #1.1 via the Live Update section of our EPP portal, we saw the message advising that the patch was successfully installed however the update still shows as available under live updates. I just wanted to reach out and confirm this was normal behavior, or if the update should no longer show up once successfully installed?

Regards,
Shawn
